history.content:
ASUC Office of Senator Sensurucu is hosting a Tech & Entrepreneurship networking event!
Come to our Startup Expo on Wednesday, December 1st, from 5-8pm to meet top student entrepreneurs, their startups and Tech & Entrepreneurship faculty at UC Berkeley! The event will take place in Tilden Hall on the 5th floor of MLK, and will provide great opportunities for networking and professional speed-dating. Dress code is casual for attendees, and business casual for student startup participants. Register as an attendee or apply as a student startup using the links below:

Register as an ATTENDEE: https://tinyurl.com/startupexpoattendee

Apply to present as a STUDENT STARTUP: https://tinyurl.com/startupexpopresenter
(APPLICATION DEADLINE is November 24th, 2021, 11:59PM Pacific Time)

ASUC Startup Expo Workshop (Info session): https://tinyurl.com/startupexpoinfosession

Facebook event link: https://fb.me/e/1QSPfC1ZY
If you have any questions, please feel free to contact ryusei.best@berkeley.edu (Director of International Affairs at Office of Senator Sensurucu).
history.subject: ASUC Startup Expo | Pitch your startup ideas and network!
